&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This hybrid position with in-office collaboration (Yonkers and/or NYC) just once per month provides excellent flexibility.&amp;nbsp; This position is not eligible for sponsorship or relocation assistance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
