&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is a Limited Duration position, expecting to end August 31, 2027.&amp;nbsp; There is a possibility that the position will be extended. The position is designated as a hybrid for in-office collaboration and meetings as needed.&amp;nbsp; This position is not eligible for sponsorship or relocation assistance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
