&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Identify, assess, and develop new business opportunities&lt;/strong&gt; — including ventures, partnerships, and business models that expand CR’s reach, impact, and sustainability.&

