&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;WHO WE ARE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Consumer Reports is an independent, nonprofit organization dedicated to a fair and just marketplace for all. CR is known for our rigorous testing and trusted ratings on thousands of products and services.&amp;nbsp; We report extensively on consumer trends and challenges, and survey millions of people in the U.S. each year. We leverage our evidence-based approach to advocate for consumer rights, working with policymakers and companies to find solutions for safer products and fair practices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our mission starts with you. We offer medical benefits that start on your first day as a CR employee that include behavioral health coverage, family planning and a generous 401K match. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.consumerreports.org/cro/careers/landing-page/index.htm&quot;&gt;Learn more about how CR advocates on behalf of our employees.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;CR’s Shopping program extends our expert recommendations beyond product selection to help consumers make smarter purchase decisions. We make it easier for people to buy the right products, at the right price, from vetted online retailers whenever they are ready to shop.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an experienced, affiliate-savvy marketer to manage the growth and day-to-day execution of our program. The Manager, Shopping will report to the Associate Director, Shopping while working directly with our affiliate partners, retailers and commerce platforms to maintain operational excellence, support partner relationships, and execute initiatives that drive revenue performance.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If you have a strong understanding of affiliate marketing models and want to use your knowledge towards shaping an equitable and safe marketplace, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is a hybrid position with anticipated monthly on-site meetings. This position is not eligible for sponsorship or relocation support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Make An Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
