&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As Senior Marketing Associate,Membership Marketing, you will play a key role in helping to grow CR&#39;s digital membership. Reporting to the Director, Digital Acquisition, you will be responsible for website and performance marketing, creative trafficking, landing page optimizations, and experimentation roadmaps.&amp;nbsp; Working cross-functionally with Product, Design, Brand Marketing, Performance Marketing, SEO and our 3P Partner Network, you will serve as the point person to lead conversion rate optimization projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If you are a creative digital marketer with strong project management skills that include collaborating with others, a strong sense of project ownership and the ability to drive high quality results while managing competing priorities, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is a hybrid position, based in Yonkers, New York. The position is not eligible for sponsorship or relocation assistance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
